<DIV1 N="145" TYPE="issue">
<HEAD>The TATLER. [N^o 145.</HEAD>
<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><L>N<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">&s;cio quis teneros Oculus mihi fa&s;cinet Agnos.</L>
<BIBL>Virg.</BIBL></Q>
