<P>Mr. <HI>Bicker&s;taff</HI>'s Aereal Me&s;&s;enger has brought him a Report of what pa&s;&s;ed at the Auction of Pictures which was in <HI>Somer&s;et</HI>-Hou&s;e Yard on <HI>Monday</HI> la&s;t, and finds there were no <HI>Screens</HI> pre&s;ent, but all tran&s;acted with great Ju&s;tice.</P>
